description:
With Milfeulle and the gate under attack, Takuto and the Angel Troupe scramble to recover Nano-Nano and the stolen emblem frame, Brave Heart, from Anise.

In the meantime, Kazuya tries to cheer up Apricot who is slowly warming up to him, but not for reasons he had hoped for.

And with their number already reduced, the former Angel Troupe leader Lily has yet to rejoin her crew. But nothing will prepare the Angel Troupe for a very sudden betrayal.
name: Vol. 2

description:
Forte Stollen hasn’t been acting like herself lately, and the Rune Angel Troupe is worried. If rumors are to be believed, then one of the original Galaxy Angels is leading a revolution! Why would Forte do such a thing? And how can she be stopped?

Things get even more complicated when Nano-Nano collapses while tending to the wounded Luxiole. But when the key to Nano-Nano’s survival lies on a distant planet that doesn't take kindly to visitors, it's going to take the help of an old friend to get out of this one!

Meanwhile, Kahlua's (or is it Tequila's?) nightmares are getting worse, and with them come memories that are best left forgotten. With the past closing in, and the future uncertain, what's an Angel to do?
name: Vol. 3

description:
When Chitose joined the Imperial Forces, she never dreamed that she'd end up working with her idols, the Angel Troupe. Now that Chitose is on the team, the Angels need her to join them for a very special mission: a Galaxy Angel vacation!

As Milfeulle and the gang get acquainted with their new teammate, the Elle Ciel is fitted with a new weapon from the White Moon. What is this strange piece of Lost Technology? Can Takuto figure out how to use it? With Milfie's luck, they'd better figure it out soon!
name: Vol. 1

description:
Secrets are revealed on the White Moon, as fragments of Chitose's past begin to surface and Prince Shiva's story is finally told.

Meanwhile, the Space Whale's picking up bad vibes, so Kuromie warns Takuto to be on alert. The Angel Troupe is up to something secretive-could they be the source?

With the discovery of a new Emblem Frame, the Angels are poised to take on Eonia once more. But when he launches his ultimate plan, hope begins to fade as the troupe is dealt a devastating blow.
name: Vol. 2

description:
The Angel Troupe has been shaken to its core. Friends can't be trusted, old secrets are revealed, and Eonia has returned. with reinforcements.

Good and evil literally collide, as the White Moon and the Black Moon are brought face to face. Nowhere is the darkness stronger than with Chitose, whose Emblem Frame has turned black with evil.

Can the Angel Troupe bear to fight one of their own? Can they stop the darkness from swallowing the light? Milfie's luck may be good, but this is gonna take a miracle.
name: Vol. 3

description:
The Angel Troupe is just about done with their current mission to deliver over a million dollars to the Bank of Transbaal, when Milfeulle accidentally opens the hatch and loses it in space. In order to keep their jobs, the Angel Troupe needs to raise money, and fast!

Read this and other exciting adventures by some of Japan’s most talented artists!
name: Vol. 1

description:
Things are getting a little weird for the Angel Troupe.

Mysterious forces haunt the Elle Ciel, wreaking havoc on Mint's favorite dessert. Worse still, the Angels are sent on a mission to the Planet of No Return, and Vanilla has to adjust to the responsibilities of motherhood. But none of this can prepare the Angels for the strangest thing of all: Forte has a date!

What kind of party is this, anyway!?
name: Vol. 2

description:
I Am Soildweller - Part I

Jack Natari has rescued his companions, Lord Kaai and the Princess Panduu, from the dungeon prison in Irisius. Riding for days across the Vastness of Blask they make camp in the wasteland a few leagues from the Citadel of Xiar.

That night Lord Kaai tells Jack a tale from ancient Raelakite lore: "The Sojourn of the Soildweller." The myth takes place in an ancient kingdom that is invaded by the evil "Sky Gods." With their kingdom ravaged and their women abducted, a prince sets out on a journey to recover his bride from captivity and is forever changed in the process.
name: I Am Soildweller Part 1
